<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <!--Placeholder name for the app, happy to take suggestions... doesn't really matter but figured we should give it one-->
    <title>PokeNode Home</title>
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css"> -->
    <style>
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

.container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

h1 {
    color: #3f51b5;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

a {
    color: #3f51b5;
    text-decoration: none;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

form {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

input[type="text"],
textarea {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
}

input[type="submit"],
input[type="reset"] {
    background-color: #3f51b5;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

input[type="submit"]:hover,
input[type="reset"]:hover {
    background-color: #303f9f;
}

hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    margin: 20px 0;
}

.notification {
    color: red;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

u {
    text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to PokeNode!</h1>
        <hr>
        <p>PokeNode is a web app that allows you to create and share custom Pokemon!</p>
        <p>Click <a href="/create">here</a> to create your own custom Pokemon!</p>
        <p>Click <a href="/findCustom">here</a> to find a custom Pokemon!</p>
        <p>Want to see all of our custom Pokemon? Click <a href="/listAll">here</a>.</p>
        <p>Need some inspiration? Click <a href="/findPokemon">here</a> to find the Pokedex entry for a real Pokemon!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
